BaseField.Name: Label52
BaseField.Text: Instructions: Tokens are pieces of information that will dynamically change in the Subject or Body of an email. In order to add a token, put the bracket [ ] symbols in the text where you want the token to display. Inside of the brackets [ ] add the token name listed below to display that data. For example, if [First Name] is listed below, you could write, "Hello [First Name]," to address the email recipient by their first name.
